Package: electivity
Type: Package
Title: Algorithms for electivity indices and measures of resource use versus availability
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Desi Quintans
Maintainer: Desi Quintans <science@desiquintans.com>
Description: This package is basically Lechowicz (1982) turned into an R package. It 
    includes all algorithms that were described therein, plus the example data that
    was provided for gypsy moth resource utilisation.
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
Depends: R (>= 3.4.0)
Suggests: utils (>= 3.4.2), usethis (>= 1.0.0)
RoxygenNote: 6.1.1
